  "reference_number": "RUS0841",
  "remarks": "\n State Councillor of the Russian Federation, 1st Class Tatiana Viktorovna SHEVTSOVA is a Deputy Minister of Defence of the Armed Forces of the Russian Federation. She is considered to have directed, or otherwise have had involvement in, responsibility for or influence over the deployment of forces involved in the Russian invasion of Ukraine. There are therefore reasonable grounds to suspect that she is a person who is responsible for, engages in, provides support for, or promotes any policy or action which destabilises Ukraine or undermines or threatens the territorial integrity, sovereignty or independence of Ukraine. \n The trust services sanctions were imposed on 21/03/2023.",
